---
---

<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-28">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="text-center">
      <span class="badge">¿Por qué FullPOS?</span>
      <h2 class="section-title mt-4">La Mejor Opción para tu Negocio</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Miles de negocios confían en FullPOS por su confiabilidad, facilidad de uso y potentes funciones.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:mt-12 sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-6">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl sm:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary transition-all duration-300 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white sm:h-14 sm:w-14">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 sm:h-7 sm:w-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636a9 9 0 010 12.728m-2.829-2.829a5 5 0 000-7.07m-4.243 4.243a1 1 0 010-1.414" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-xl">Funciona Sin Internet</h3>
            <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 sm:mt-2 sm:text-base">Continúa vendiendo aunque falle tu conexión a internet. FullPOS funciona completamente offline, tus datos están seguros en tu computadora.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl sm:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/10 text-accent transition-all duration-300 group-hover:bg-accent group-hover:text-white sm:h-14 sm:w-14">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 sm:h-7 sm:w-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-xl">Reportes desde tu Celular</h3>
            <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 sm:mt-2 sm:text-base">Revisa ventas e inventario desde tu teléfono con FullPOS Owner. Accede a informes en tiempo real desde cualquier lugar.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl sm:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-green-500/10 text-green-500 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:bg-green-500 group-hover:text-white sm:h-14 sm:w-14">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 sm:h-7 sm:w-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 10h4.764a2 2 0 011.789 2.894l-3.5 7A2 2 0 0115.263 21h-4.017c-.163 0-.326-.02-.485-.06L7 20m7-10V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-.095c-.5 0-.905.405-.905.905 0 .714-.211 1.412-.608 2.006L7 11v9m7-10h-2M7 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2h2.5" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-xl">Fácil de Aprender</h3>
            <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 sm:mt-2 sm:text-base">Interfaz simple e intuitiva. Tus empleados aprenderán a usar FullPOS en cuestión de horas, no de días.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl sm:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-500 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:bg-purple-500 group-hover:text-white sm:h-14 sm:w-14">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 sm:h-7 sm:w-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-xl">Soporte Técnico</h3>
            <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 sm:mt-2 sm:text-base">Instalación y soporte profesional. Te ayudamos a configurar FullPOS, importar tus datos y capacitar a tu equipo.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
